 do not get a discrete spectrum of KK states, and we conclude that the\nclaim that Weylian structures mimic, classically, quantum behaviour does not\nconstitute a generic feature of these geometric manifolds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2005 03:32:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
