estimation procedure, in particular, when a choice\nof $w_{\\theta}$ depending on $\\theta$ would be more appropriate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2005 12:33:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Jun 2008 13:06:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-29"}
